Package: RankUni
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Extracting University Ranking Data from the web
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Inmaculada", "RM",
      email = "inma@fitovitalia.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: An R package providing functions to scrape, extract, and organize data from major university ranking websites, 
  with a focus on UK university rankings. 
  The package enables automated data collection for research, analysis, and visualization of academic performance metrics across multiple ranking platforms.
